content:
Create a reusable promotion template:
Use the new PromotionTemplate object.
Create stages for a promotion template:
Use the new PromotionStageTemplate object.
Use a promotion template to create a promotion:
Use the new PromotionTemplateId field on the existing Promotion object.
Specify at which stage of a promotion's advocates and their referred friends are rewarded:
Use the new ReferrerJournalSubTypeId and ReferredPartyJournalSubTypeId fields on the existing PromotionStage object.
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes for Referral Marketing
